OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAnother very hot day across
OL,6,Fmuch of England and Wales with strong
OL,7,Fsunshine. Fresher across northern
OL,8,Fareas with sunny spells. A few
OL,9,Fthundery showers may bubble up across
OL,10,FEngland and Wales later in the
OL,11,Fafternoon with intense downpours.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAn easterly breeze will
OL,14,Fgradually develop overnight, drawing
OL,15,Fin fresher air to eastern areas.
OL,16,FStaying dry but turning cloudier
OL,17,Facross the northeast. Staying rather
OL,18,Fwarm in the southwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
