OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FDry on Wednesday with sunny
OL,6,Fspells for many. Cloudier in the
OL,7,Fnortheast but some bright spells
OL,8,Fslowly developing. Very warm in the
OL,9,Fsouthwest, but feeling fresher
OL,10,Felsewhere.
